data.description: Upgraded with granite kitchen counters, piedrafina bath counters, tile floors in the entry, kitchen, dining, bathrooms, and laundry. Upgraded carpet throughout, custom stained cabinets, and upgraded stainless steel kitchen aid appliances. Included in sale, front load washer/dryer, garage storage racks, new freezer in garage, epoxied garage floors. This charming home is in a gated community with dog park within walking distance. Two swimming pools, one is open year round as well as the hot tub! The mountain views are stunning from the 1st and 2nd floor of the home! There are so many extra's with this home! Buyer and buyers agent to verify all information provided.
